Once upon a time in a forrest there lived a monkey who recieded on a berry tree which was on the banks of a river in the same forrest there lived a crocodile and his wife. 
One day the crocodile came to the banks of the river adn rested under the tree, the kind hearted monkey offerd him some fruits.
The crocodile came back the next day for some more fruits as he loved them, as days passed by crocodile and monkey become friends.